VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'with black mist. &gt;&gt; Okay. And obviously you\'re going to have a pricing for kits and individual filters. What what are we looking at for in the range? &gt;&gt; So the the ultimate kit is about 280. Each individual filter around 60, 70'

